dct_title_s: Asia Minor 1:250.000: Mersina. Series G.S.G.S. no. 2097
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes glossary of topographical terms (in English and Turkish). Map is part of a set of 30 sheets. Each sheet includes "Index to adjoining sheets". Alternate title: Asia Minor: Mersina. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Glossary of terms in Turkish and English. Map is part of a set of 30 sheet. For holdings see index. Alaya, Alaia, or Alaiye is now called Alanya. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 2097.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: [Southampton] : War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section, 1916.
